body: Can you try `pip install --upgrade tf-nightly-gpu` to pull a later version of tensorflow? Looking at the version number, it seems out of date (20180330 - the changes were only made on 4/20). You should have a version number like `tf-nightly-gpu 1.9.0.dev20180426`
